{"arkId":"cl010492662","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010492662","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"Corbeille \u00e0 fruits","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Corbeille \u00e0 fruits"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1638 - 1639","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 521 - Bernard Palissy, Vitrine 5","room":"Salle 521, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1638,"endYear":1639,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Chrestien, Nicolas","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2021.42.1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; corbeille","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La corbeille circulaire et peu profonde repose sur une petite base. L\u0027ensemble est ajour\u00e9 avec des motifs d\u00e9coratifs estamp\u00e9s pr\u00e9sentant des reprises en ciselure. Le d\u00e9cor est constitu\u00e9 de godrons, d\u0027enroulements et de cartouches compos\u00e9s de paniers de fruits encadr\u00e9s de rinceaux de feuillages. L\u0027 aile large et plate est agr\u00e9ment\u00e9e de deux anses horizontales fondues et cisel\u00e9es repr\u00e9sentant une guirlande de fleurs et de fruits sur laquelle vient picorer un oiseau. Au fond, autour de l\u2019ombilic grav\u00e9 du cartouche armori\u00e9 rayonnent six grands godrons ponctu\u00e9s de granulations, dispos\u00e9s en alternance avec six motifs d\u2019enroulements fleuronn\u00e9s et reperc\u00e9s. La dorure est sans doute post\u00e9rieure au XVIIe si\u00e8cle.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Armes de Sir Richard Neave (1731-1814), gouverneur de la Banque d\u2019Angleterre en 1780 et cr\u00e9\u00e9 1er baronnet le 13 mai 1795, ou de son fils Sir Thomas Neave (1761-1848) (Grav\u00e9es au centre)\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Ma\u00eetre : fleur de lis couronn\u00e9e, deux grains, lettres N et X avec un c\u0153ur dans un croissant au centre, pour Nicolas Crestien ; Jurande : lettre S couronn\u00e9e pour Paris, d\u00e9cembre 1638-d\u00e9cembre 1639","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,5","displayDimension":"5,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"40,7","displayDimension":"40,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"31,1","displayDimension":"31,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9 (reperc\u00e9)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Baronnets Neave au XIXe si\u00e8cle ; vente Important European Silver, Christie\u2019s Gen\u00e8ve, 15 mai 1995, n\u00b0168 ; collection de Lord Harris de Peckham (vente Christie\u2019s, Londres, 25 novembre 2008, n\u00b0 6) ; vente en ligne The Exceptional Sale, Christie\u2019s, 23 novembre 2021, n\u00b0 235.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"01\/12\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"Commission acquisition","value":"01\/12\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de l\u0027inscription sur l\u0027inventaire","value":"10\/12\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de 